      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "GetBalance receives `bool avoid_reuse` in the last argument, should not be `true` or just remove the if condition directly and pass the result of `IsWalletFlagSet(WALLET_FLAG_AVOID_REUSE)` entirely.\r\n```suggestion\r\n            const auto full_bal = GetBalance(*m_wallet, 0, true);\r\n```",
